flowchart TD
  start([Incoming /api/v1 request]) --> mode{AUTH_BOUNDARY_MODE}

  mode -->|stub| stub[Allow request\nAttach mode metadata]
  mode -->|enforced| token{Token valid?}

  token -->|yes| authorize[Authorize\nAttach identity context]
  token -->|no| deny[Return 401/403\nStructured error]

  stub --> corr[Resolve correlation id]
  authorize --> corr
  corr --> route[Dispatch to domain proxy module]
  route --> done([Passthrough response])
  deny --> end([Stop])

  note1[Enforced mode remains integration-agnostic:\nany token provider implementing validation contract can be used]
  mode -.-> note1
